                  Barrett</persname></unittitle>
            <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1965 Jan 23</unitdate>
            <physdesc>TLS, 1 p.</physdesc>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>[Acknowledges Barrett's letter concerning his
                  appreciation of her book and supplies an itinerary of
                  her planned research trip.]</p>
          </scopecontent>
